(36, 1, '2020-01-03 10:51:50', '2020-01-03 10:51:50', 'Sea view annex is a three-kilometer long, beautiful cove of white sand, secluded in the palms. Also known as the silent beach, Agonda is the undiscovered paradise of Goa. Sea view annex beach is the ideal place to laze and relax as not many tourists visit this area. The nature is at its best here with the beautiful sea, a background of palms and YOU in the midst of it.', 'SEA VIEW ANNEX', 'We have two types of beach view huts on the ground, and on an elevated wooden platform.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'sea-view-annex', '', '', '2020-01-13 11:55:00', '2020-01-13 11:55:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/agondawp/?post_type=mphb_room_type&#038;p=36', 0, 'mphb_room_type', '', 0),
